noncomputable def LocPathConnectedSpace (X : Type*) [TopologicalSpace X] : Prop :=
  ∀ x y : X, ∃ (f : Icc x y → X), Continuous f ∧
  ∀ x y : X, ∃ (f : Icc x y → X), Continuous f ∧
  ∀ U : Set X, IsOpen U → U ≠ ⊥ →
  (∃ (f : Icc (x : Icc x y) y → X), Continuous f ∧
  ∀ x ∈ U, ∃ y ∈ U, x ≠ y → ∃ (f : Icc x y → X), Continuous f)

  -- Note: uses (u : Set X) instead of (U : Set X) because of a technicality in the original statement
  
  
  LocPathConnectedSpace X = LocPathConnectedSpace (Set.univ : Set X)
